---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---
<Layout region="na" title="Home">
  <section class="bg-[#E7F1F2] py-16 lg:py-20">
    <div class="mx-auto flex max-w-6xl flex-col gap-10 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:flex-row lg:items-center lg:px-8">
      <!-- Left: text -->
      <div class="max-w-xl">
        <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-slate-600">
          Decision-ready site reality
        </p>
        <h1 class="mt-3 text-4xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-slate-900 sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl">
          As-Built Surveys Across the US &amp; Canada
        </h1>
        <p class="mt-4 text-sm sm:text-base text-slate-700 leading-relaxed">
          We document real-world conditions and deliver a digital twin + detailed report in a few business days, so you cut change orders, protect budgets, and make faster lease decisions.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-2 text-xs text-slate-500">
          All site data is captured and structured using our internal ScopeWalk™ platform.
        </p>

        <!-- Primary actions -->
        <div class="mt-6 flex flex-wrap gap-3">
          <a
            href="/contact"
            class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-[#B48A3C] px-5 py-2.5 text-sm font-medium text-white shadow-sm hover:bg-[#9b7532]"
          >
            Book a site visit
          </a>
          <a
            href="/pricing"
            class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-full border border-slate-300 bg-white/80 px-5 py-2.5 text-sm font-medium text-slate-800 hover:bg-white"
          >
            View pricing
          </a>
        </div>

        <!-- Small stat chips -->
        <div class="mt-5 flex flex-wrap gap-2 text-[11px] font-medium text-slate-700">
          <span class="inline-flex items-center rounded-full bg-white/70 px-3 py-1">
            500+ commercial site visits
          </span>
          <span class="inline-flex items-center rounded-full bg-white/70 px-3 py-1">
            3–5 day typical turnaround
          </span>
          <span class="inline-flex items-center rounded-full bg-white/70 px-3 py-1">
            Across 48+ states &amp; provinces
          </span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Right: key points + image -->
      <div class="flex-1">
        <div class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white/95 p-5 shadow-sm backdrop-blur transition-colors hover:border-accent hover:shadow-md hover:shadow-accent/20">
          <h2 class="text-sm font-semibold text-slate-900">
            Every visit includes
          </h2>
          <ul class="mt-3 space-y-2 text-sm text-slate-700">
            <li class="flex gap-2">
              <span class="mt-1 h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-[#0F2A43]"></span>
              <span>Digital twin or 360&deg; walkthrough + labeled photo storyboard.</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-2">
              <span class="mt-1 h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-[#0F2A43]"></span>
              <span>Detailed conditions report with fixture counts and a high-level MEP overview.</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-2">
              <span class="mt-1 h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-[#0F2A43]"></span>
              <span>Nationwide US &amp; Canada coverage with predictable, all-in pricing.</span>
            </li>
          </ul>

          <!-- Hero image: report + twin -->
          <div class="mt-4 overflow-hidden rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-slate-900/5">
            <img
              src="/Images/Presentation1.jpg"
              alt="Example Alturascope digital twin and site reality report"
              class="h-full w-full object-cover"
            />
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="bg-[#0F2A43]">
    <div class="mx-auto flex max-w-6xl flex-col gap-4 px-4 py-6 text-sm text-slate-100 sm:flex-row sm:items-center sm:justify-between sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div>
        <p class="font-semibold">
          Built for design-build &amp; GC partners, Landlords, Brokers, and PE-backed roll-outs.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-1 text-xs text-slate-200/80">
          Independent and vendor-neutral—no construction to sell, just clear site reality you can use for leases, capex decisions, and lenders.
        </p>
      </div>
      <a
        href="#how-it-works"
        class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-full border border-slate-100/40 px-5 py-2 text-xs font-medium text-slate-50 hover:bg-slate-50 hover:text-[#0F2A43]"
      >
        See how we work
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="border-t border-slate-100 bg-white">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-4 py-6 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-slate-50 px-5 py-4 text-sm text-slate-800 shadow-sm transition-colors hover:border-accent hover:shadow-md hover:shadow-accent/20">
        <p class="font-medium">
          Why invest in detailed as-built reality?
        </p>
        <p class="mt-1 text-slate-700">
          A site visit is one of the smallest costs in the project and one of the biggest levers on risk—cutting change orders, protecting dates, and helping you avoid bad buildings.
          <a href="/why-as-built-surveys-matter" class="ml-1 font-medium text-[#0F2A43] underline underline-offset-2">
            Learn how it pays for itself.
          </a>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- HOW IT WORKS -->
  <section id="how-it-works" class="py-12 lg:py-16">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="max-w-3xl">
        <h2 class="text-base font-bold uppercase tracking-wide text-slate-800">
          How it works
        </h2>
        <p class="mt-2 text-lg font-semibold tracking-tight text-slate-900">
          A simple, repeatable process on every site.
        </p>
      </div>
      <ol class="mt-6 grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-4">
        <li class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-4 text-sm text-slate-700 shadow-sm transition-colors hover:border-accent hover:shadow-md hover:shadow-accent/20">
          <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-slate-500">Step 1</p>
          <p class="mt-1 font-medium text-slate-900">Clarify the decision</p>
          <p class="mt-1 text-xs leading-relaxed">
            We align on what you’re deciding&mdash;renew vs. relocate, fund vs. defer, re-use vs. rebuild&mdash;and
            what your team needs to see.
          </p>
        </li>
        <li class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-4 text-sm text-slate-700 shadow-sm transition-colors hover:border-accent hover:shadow-md hover:shadow-accent/20">
          <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-slate-500">Step 2</p>
          <p class="mt-1 font-medium text-slate-900">Lock access &amp; dates</p>
          <p class="mt-1 text-xs leading-relaxed">
            We coordinate with building management, security, and your stakeholders, then book travel under our
            national flight pass.
          </p>
        </li>
        <li class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-4 text-sm text-slate-700 shadow-sm transition-colors hover:border-accent hover:shadow-md hover:shadow-accent/20">
          <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-slate-500">Step 3</p>
          <p class="mt-1 font-medium text-slate-900">Capture the reality</p>
          <p class="mt-1 text-xs leading-relaxed">
            On site we follow a disciplined route to document structure, services, access, and any conditions
            that affect design, cost, or schedule. On-site visuals, notes, measurements, and observations are captured in real time using our internal ScopeWalk™ system, ensuring consistent structure and clarity across every visit.
          </p>
        </li>
        <li class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-4 text-sm text-slate-700 shadow-sm transition-colors hover:border-accent hover:shadow-md hover:shadow-accent/20">
          <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-slate-500">Step 4</p>
          <p class="mt-1 font-medium text-slate-900">Deliver decision-ready outputs</p>
          <p class="mt-1 text-xs leading-relaxed">
            You receive a digital twin, labeled photos, and a detailed report with fixture counts, a high-level
            mechanical overview, and prioritised recommendations.
          </p>
        </li>
      </ol>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- WHAT YOU RECEIVE EVERY VISIT -->
  <section class="py-12 lg:py-16 bg-slate-50">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="max-w-3xl">
        <h2 class="text-base font-bold uppercase tracking-wide text-slate-800">
          Deliverables
        </h2>
        <p class="mt-2 text-lg font-semibold tracking-tight text-slate-900">
          What you receive on every visit.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-600">
          Same structure, every time&mdash;so your team can line sites up side-by-side and move quickly.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="mt-6 grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-2">
        <article class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm transition-colors hover:border-accent hover:shadow-md hover:shadow-accent/20">
          <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-slate-700">
            Visuals
          </h3>
          <ul class="mt-3 list-disc space-y-1 pl-5 text-sm text-slate-700">
            <li>Digital twin or 360° walkthrough of the space</li>
            <li>Full, detailed video walkthrough with narration</li>
            <li>Labeled photo storyboard by area and topic</li>
            <li>Context shots of access, loading, parking, neighbors</li>
            <li>Optional drone stills &amp; clips where allowed</li>
          </ul>
        </article>
        <article class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm transition-colors hover:border-accent hover:shadow-md hover:shadow-accent/20">
          <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-slate-700">
            Documentation
          </h3>
          <ul class="mt-3 list-disc space-y-1 pl-5 text-sm text-slate-700">
            <li>Detailed measurements according to brief</li>
            <li>Fixture &amp; services counts (lights, diffusers, sprinklers, doors, WCs, key equipment)</li>
            <li>Detailed written conditions report with a high-level mechanical / services overview</li>
            <li>Upsides and concerns clearly highlighted</li>
            <li>Recommendations prioritised into P1 / P2 / P3 so you know what to act on first</li>
          </ul>
        </article>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- WHO WE WORK WITH & WHERE -->
  <section class="py-12 lg:py-16">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="grid gap-8 md:grid-cols-[minmax(0,1.3fr)_minmax(0,1.7fr)]">
        <article>
          <h2 class="text-base font-bold uppercase tracking-wide text-slate-800">
            Who we work with
          </h2>
          <p class="mt-2 text-lg font-semibold tracking-tight text-slate-900">
            Built for teams making decisions on space at scale.
          </p>
          <div class="mt-4 flex flex-wrap gap-2 text-xs font-medium text-slate-800">
            <span class="rounded-full bg-slate-100 px-3 py-1">Landlords &amp; asset managers</span>
            <span class="rounded-full bg-slate-100 px-3 py-1">Tenants &amp; workplace teams</span>
            <span class="rounded-full bg-slate-100 px-3 py-1">Brokers &amp; project managers</span>
            <span class="rounded-full bg-slate-100 px-3 py-1">Private equity &amp; lenders</span>
            <span class="rounded-full bg-slate-100 px-3 py-1">Design-build &amp; GC partners</span>
          </div>
          <p class="mt-4 text-xs text-slate-500">
            Typical use cases include pre-lease diligence, renew-vs-relocate analysis, rollout
            programmes, independent progress verification, and lender / investor updates.
          </p>
        </article>
        <article class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm transition-colors hover:border-accent hover:shadow-md hover:shadow-accent/20">
          <h2 class="text-base font-bold uppercase tracking-wide text-slate-800">
            Where we operate
          </h2>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-700">
            Alturascope currently covers <span class="font-medium">the United States and Canada</span>
            under a national flight-pass model.
          </p>
          <ul class="mt-3 list-disc space-y-1 pl-5 text-sm text-slate-700">
            <li>Major metros, secondary markets, and many tertiary locations</li>
            <li>Office, flex, industrial, retail, and healthcare / clinic spaces</li>
            <li>One-off sites or multi-market portfolios</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="mt-3 text-xs text-slate-500">
            Looking for coverage in the United Kingdom?
            <a href="/uk" class="font-medium text-[#0F2A43] underline underline-offset-2">
              Visit Alturascope UK
            </a>
            for U.K.-specific services and pricing.
          </p>
        </article>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- MINI USE CASES / \"THIS IS WHAT WE HELPED WITH\" -->
  <section class="py-12 lg:py-16 bg-slate-50">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-4 sm:flex-row sm:items-end sm:justify-between">
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-slate-500">
            Example engagements
          </h2>
          <p class="mt-2 text-lg font-semibold tracking-tight text-slate-900">
            Where Alturascope fits into real projects.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="mt-6 grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-3">
        <article class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm transition-colors hover:border-accent hover:shadow-md hover:shadow-accent/20">
          <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-slate-500">
            Renew vs. relocate
          </p>
          <h3 class="mt-2 text-sm font-semibold text-slate-900">
            Office landlord with expiring lease
          </h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-700">
            We documented an existing tenant space and two alternatives, highlighting base-build gaps,
            services constraints, and quick-win upgrades so the asset team could structure a renewal
            that made financial sense.
          </p>
        </article>
      <article class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm transition-colors hover:border-accent hover:shadow-md hover:shadow-accent/20">
          <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-slate-500">
            Roll-out readiness
          </p>
          <h3 class="mt-2 text-sm font-semibold text-slate-900">
            Behavioural health &amp; clinic expansion
          </h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-700">
            For a PE-backed clinic group, we captured new locations before lease and construction,
            checking bathroom counts, access, and services to support their programme and lender
            requirements.
          </p>
        </article>
      <article class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm transition-colors hover:border-accent hover:shadow-md hover:shadow-accent/20">
          <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-slate-500">
            Lender &amp; investor support
          </p>
          <h3 class="mt-2 text-sm font-semibold text-slate-900">
            Independent progress verification
          </h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-700">
            We provided fixed-route progress photography, a digital twin, and exceptions log so a
            lender could track risk on a renovation draw schedule without flying their own team in.
          </p>
        </article>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FINAL CTA STRIP -->
  <section class="py-12">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-slate-50 px-6 py-8 sm:flex sm:items-center sm:justify-between shadow-sm transition-colors hover:border-accent hover:shadow-md hover:shadow-accent/20">
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900">
            Ready to move a site forward?
          </h2>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-600">
            Share the address, approximate size, and what you’re deciding. We’ll confirm the scope,
            recommend the right visit type, and send a simple, all-in quote.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="mt-4 flex flex-wrap gap-3 sm:mt-0 sm:justify-end">
          <a
            href="/contact"
            class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-[#0F2A43] px-5 py-2.5 text-sm font-medium text-white shadow-sm hover:bg-slate-900"
          >
            Book a site visit
          </a>
          <a
            href="/pricing"
            class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-full border border-slate-300 px-5 py-2.5 text-sm font-medium text-slate-800 hover:bg-white"
          >
            View pricing
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
